5.	Clary, E.G. & Snyder, M. (1999). The motivations to volunteer: Theoretical and practical considerations. Current Directions in Psychological Science, 8(5), pp. 156-159.
6.	Schein, E.H. (2010). Organizational culture and leadership. 4th ed. San Francisco: Jossey-Bass.
